Author: oldangst
Text: I feel the exact same way... people probably don't think anything of me when they look at me, my body proportions are really unfortunate so I just look... small (of course i dont really think that) but not sick. and i wonder if i ever will look like i am. Ive never even passed out before and I dont get dizzy and I get my periods normally and as much as that is good, I feel so invalid and gross because that makes me "healthy."
